his gives a high robustness to this coordination\nmechanism.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Dec 2017 18:06:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 6 Jul 2018 20:09:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-27"}
